<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvela albang ka vaihlai in,
 Hin leh dam valbang ka khuolna'n;
 Chungleng Zuomang min ka siel leh,
 Setan nuoi zinmangpa'n,
 Tawngka nau bang a sang.

[V2]
 2. Israelte'n mang bang paih mah leu,
 Holemin zinbang tha puong ie;
 Zion Lalmang thisan pal lun,
 Lo ing ie ziet tiengin,
 Chulmawh a tuoilo din.

[V3]
 3. Ngilhmawh tuoinih thum leh chin-ngaihte,
 Thisana zinbang na koh te;
 Lungtupa sula a lengte,
 Lengvan tuolpi nuomah;
 Ni banga lun dingin.

[V4]
 4. Setan sausuon thim bang zing nuoiah,
 Krista'n khawvel chu A e'n tai;
 A tawngdam nau bang ka sang tai,
 Ihmut khang thei ka lo;
 Thavang lim bang ka bel.

[V5]
 5. Miza'n chawngsum bang niel mah leu le,
 Gam zangpi guobang ka hinna;
 Thing Kraws lela Zuomang vawnchawih,
 Lungin ngilh zo puong ie;
 Lunglun aw, Lal Krista.</lyrics>
<title>Albang Vaihna Khawvel</title>
<author>Kawpsawng</author>
<hymn_number>152</hymn_number>
</song>